{"tid":1000030,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"曼德拉效應 同 時空穿梭有關？？","createTime":"2019-01-29T06:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T06:08:13.000Z","uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"abbe109063602a716ccf86a61320dce99f1d6312","tid":1000030,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"時空穿梭因而引發出曼德拉效應？？<br />\n<br />\n原理係：利用時光機回到過去<br />\n搞亂我哋認知嘅歷史<br />\n繼而引發曼德拉效應<br />\n<br />\n話說，蔡楓華其實一直都係講「一剎那光輝唔代表永恆」<br />\n而有人搭時光機返去搞亂左個歷史<br />\n結果金句出現改變<br />\n個理解分裂成去另一個平行宇宙<br />\n<br />\n其實都唔止係一次<br />\n甘迺迪，美國自由神像位置<br />\n一次又一次咁挑戰人類對歷史認知嘅記憶 ......"},{"pid":"f21419b59014bfa6870a52aaf165749fa29ef1c8","tid":1000030,"uid":61748,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:58:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff69a8962c68cc49a891e985c809945d5d12149b","tid":1000030,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:59:11.000Z","msg":"曼德拉效應真係好古怪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328991c37e03606759db887ceb2846d95cd4ce3c","tid":1000030,"uid":16065,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:00:34.000Z","msg":"冇記性都吹到曼加拉效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b9f70621b91e8a01acdd9201caf74ab0c41b41","tid":1000030,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:01:07.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"02436ad846f4b417daa86a78cc8ad82d430dd2b6","tid":1000030,"uid":225636,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:06:06.000Z","msg":"一直覺得孟加拉效應好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788c01deedc73f4b1ec1d80ba57e3dc3d5844977","tid":1000030,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:40:15.000Z","msg":"馬尼拉效應"},{"pid":"e60757afc6f1b6ce448aabb39ac1ed1e8c28b8ee","tid":1000030,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"簡稱 記錯"},{"pid":"6548cc8cb6137bb2a68c6fa5069b03ff5bbd1f5a","tid":1000030,"uid":86125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T08:42:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8f59de800202f1d16d2e339409c6ddfa359c1d6","tid":1000030,"uid":28603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T12:35:48.000Z","msg":"樓主返錫安教返到傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14e1375819866f9a6f6cf9b123cdb24a6d505ad","tid":1000030,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T19:21:32.000Z","msg":"孟加拉效應就孟加拉效應啦"},{"pid":"e0bfa88e82ba211c6a40549f2f973f8dfd8e977a","tid":1000030,"uid":52520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T20:05:15.000Z","msg":"其實人腦記錯野係唔出奇  <br />\n<br />\n唔好講話  點解同一時間咁多人記錯   <br />\n<br />\n有幾出奇  係我打緊呢篇文既同時我諗都有數以百萬計既人同時柯屎啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  記錯好出奇？"},{"pid":"db873d26628d4cf7e78c650b77382c37a71d01a4","tid":1000030,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:31:52.000Z","msg":"係以前adidas 係addidas 有兩個d"},{"pid":"e8ea9b52980e5cb129de8501afd4b15c120700de","tid":1000030,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係全部人一齊記錯<br />\n而係大部分人都覺得呢樣野唔重要唔care<br />\n腦入面就會覺得 你話咩咪咩囖<br />\n咁你一開始就水人講個假事實出黎<br />\n人地咪會自動以為自己都係咁記得"},{"pid":"485c1d809c0c3c0e85fbc1e8c1a54d9cc37c6a91","tid":1000030,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:40:22.000Z","msg":"尼古拉效應"},{"pid":"8704866c2b17a9e1dc21e5cd33f8a343661ed83c","tid":1000030,"uid":52511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"月經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1ecc097bc0be519a3a6e7ee4aa532e76fabe43","tid":1000030,"uid":155558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:08:13.000Z","msg":"得閒睇下外國啲科學家點講。<br />\n<br />\n有科學家試過問一個人嘅父母，問佢個仔/女細個時候發生過嘅特別事件。例如有九件事，咁科學家另外再加多一件事，係個仔/女細個時完全無發生過嘅（例如吹水話佢哋細個喺某商場走失咗，搵好耐先搵得返）。<br />\n<br />\n之後科學家同呢啲仔/女講返細個發生過嘅特別事件，好奇怪，明明無發生過嘅一項，啲仔/女竟然話有印象。<br />\n<br />\n科學家叫呢種做false memory，係人嘅大腦記憶出錯。"}]}